     H            Y/                                    1
      **** GDIR60 ****************************************************
      *  YEARLY UPDAT HANDLING
      *     G.B.C                              97/03/06
      ****************************************************************
      ****************************************************************
     FGDIPL20 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGDIWP60 IF  E                    DISK                      A
      ****************************************************************
      *発注実績
     I            DS
     I                                        1   40WKYY
     I                                        1   4 WKDATE
      ****************************************************************
      *           ＭＡＩＮ　ＲＯＵＴＩＮＥ                         *
      ****************************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PPUSER 10
     C                     PARM           PPDATE  4
     C                     PARM           PPGO    2
      ****************************************************************
     C                     MOVELPPDATE    WKDATE
     C           WKYY      SUB  5         WKYY2   40
     C                     SETOF                     50
      *
B1   C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ GDIPL20                  90
     C   90                LEAVE
      *
 B2  C           IJJSYY    IFGE WKYY2
     C                     LEAVE
 E2  C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     50
     C                     WRITEGDIPP201
E1   C                     ENDDO
      * <終　了>
     C           @END      TAG
     C   50                MOVE 'GO'      PPGO
     C  N50                MOVE 'NG'      PPGO
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      * DUMMY READ
     C                     READ GDIWP60                  90
